  <answer><![CDATA[<p>Swiss Passes gives you unlimited travel on the entire Swiss travel network included for 4, 8 or 15 consecutive days, and are available to pre-book at a supplement from £169 2nd class. These are a great option for guest wishing to explore outside the region they are staying in, to see more of Switzerland. If you are looking to stay within the region, we recommend pre-booking a regional pass if available – see individual resort pages for information.</p>
<p>When booking a Swiss Pass, the transfer ticket (incl. Half-Fare Travel Card) is still issued to cover your journeys to/from the airport.</p>]]></answer>
